OL,5, Brewdog boss James Watt has set out    
OL,6, plans to give away nearly a fifth of   
OL,7, his equity stake to the firm's staff.  
OL,9,FMr Watt owns a quarter of the          
OL,10,Ffast-growing Aberdeenshire-based beer  
OL,11,Fmaker.                                 
OL,13,FBrewery and pub workers have criticised
OL,14,Fhim over his behaviour and pressure on 
OL,15,Fthem to grow the firm rapidly.         
OL,17,FAt least partly in response, Mr Watt   
OL,18,Fhas set out an incentive plan which    
OL,19,Falso means half of its pub profits will
OL,20,Fgo to those who work on hourly rates in
OL,21,Fits 111 bars worldwide.                
